/>\n<br />\n2. The traffic system is non-existent. Cars still gets across in what light is on.<br />\n<br />\n3. Scammers everywhere. I have been scammed for a photo for 40euro (failed). Just don&rsquo;t talk to anyone approaching you <br />\n<br />\n4. Buildings are old and ugly. Not old and elegant like Paris but old and ugly. Zero urban planning, shops just randomly spread across the city. The only place is city-like place is the train terminus which like I said make you instantly regret once you step out<br />\n<br />\nI will add more if I can think of any"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T21:13:00.000Z","msg":"歐洲度度都係咁<br />\n睇住 自己小心添<br />\nD人渣槍搵食<br />\n呢5年唔好去歐洲同中東啦!<br />\n佢地又窮又懶<br />\n有D人仲以為歐洲好好 中國好差 其實差天共地 我只會心裡會恥笑佢地井底"},{"pid":"b38211949dae6ad22c52c59bf8f3e08f0f3a57b5","tid":1178974,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416202f6c1ddf2ca98ca188fd6397106fa1581ae","tid":1178974,"uid":47710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9da907e874a09ab8fe06627da250582310c08c25","tid":1178974,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84343a49d88ad94c737ec7ba8c901d6148c22e4c","tid":1178974,"uid":47710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T21:02:37.000Z","msg":"athens先係大佬 去完一次以後不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T21:05:08.000Z","msg":"俾你地咁講直頭唔想去，可唔可以講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T21:09:10.000Z","msg":"條街落後過羅馬 路又爛 成個城市陰陰沈沈咁 景點個個差唔多 條街勁多南亞裔 行過會係咁𥄫住你 勁驚<br />\n但greece嚟講santorini係值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T21:14:26.000Z","msg":"santorini好多日本人去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nathens真係狗也不屌 <br />\n衰過深水埗鴨寮街 景點收費又貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0652d735a952f26aa9ea6b614c0f82c3ed1c5f","tid":1178974,"uid